title: Sutton United 0 Arsenal 2: Sutton’s magical FA Cup run is ended as Theo Walcott bags his 100 Arsenal goal in gritty encounter
text:
EFL HEADS HELD HIGH Sutton United 0 Arsenal 2: Sutton’s magical FA Cup run is ended as Theo Walcott bags his 100 Arsenal goal in gritty encounter 
The National League outfit battled hard, even hitting the crossbar in the second half, but ultimately fell short in their huge game by JOHN HUTCHINSON
